item.description:
How do we stay high, happy and tuned in? That is a great question. Come and share what you have experienced and learn some techniques to keep the ball rolling. Learn how to stop the negative vibrations/feelings when you begin to feel them take over your mind/body. We will learn to do some tapping on the meridians that run throughout the body.
We have a guest speaker joining us to explain what Emotional Freedom Technique.
Cheri Valentine. Life Coach and Inspirational Leader, will share with us how to use a simple tapping process to remove negative emotions that are hidden your your body. I have personally worked one on one with Cheri's and she has assisted me in amazing changes in short amount of time. Join us to learn this easy and take away technique!!!
